[[All my 2020 art work]] The year 2020 was a very challenging year for everyone.However, In bad times, good things always happen.
Every art work makes me remember the story of that time well.
Thank you for everything for the past year.
Thanks to everyone who followed and liked my work. 
Let's move forward in 2021.
